# ELEVATOR SYSTEM - Requirements & Entities
## Amazon SDE2 LLD Interview Prep

---

## 🎯 Problem Statement
Design an **Elevator System** for a building with:
- Multiple floors
- Multiple elevators
- Handle external requests (floor buttons) and internal requests (destination buttons)
- Efficient scheduling/dispatching

---

## 🗣️ Clarifying Questions & Answers

### 1. WHO — Actors

| Actor | Role |
|-------|------|
| **Passenger** | Requests elevator, enters destination |
| **Elevator** | Moves between floors, serves requests |
| **ElevatorController** | Dispatches requests to elevators |

---

### 2. WHAT — Request Types

| Request Type | Where | Example |
|--------------|-------|---------|
| **External Request** | Floor button (UP/DOWN) | Person at Floor 5 presses UP |
| **Internal Request** | Inside elevator | Person in elevator presses Floor 8 |

