## 💡 Design Patterns

| Pattern | Where | Why |
|---------|-------|-----|
| **State** | Elevator behavior changes by state | Different actions in IDLE vs MOVING |
| **Strategy** | Dispatch algorithm | Swap scheduling algorithms |
| **Singleton** | ElevatorController | One controller for building |
| **Observer** | Display updates | Optional - notify floor displays |

