## 🎬 Use Cases

### Use Case 1: External Request (Floor Button)
1. Person at Floor 5 presses UP
2. Controller receives request (floor=5, direction=UP)
3. Dispatcher selects Elevator 1 (nearest, going up)
4. Elevator 1 adds Floor 5 to stops
5. Elevator 1 arrives, opens door

### Use Case 2: Internal Request (Destination)
1. Person inside Elevator 1 presses Floor 8
2. Elevator 1 adds Floor 8 to stops
3. Elevator 1 arrives at Floor 8, opens door

### Use Case 3: Multiple Requests
1. Person at Floor 2 presses UP
2. Person at Floor 7 presses DOWN
3. Dispatcher assigns different elevators based on strategy

